{"tid":619017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家南極成功種菜冀助太空人火星自種糧食","createTime":"2018-04-06T09:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T14:13:18.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c880f28d4bbf3b56aa812af63bfdab4403e1df3","tid":619017,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180406/_2018040614345552947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180406%2F_2018040614345552947.jpg&h=e755084b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">科學家南極成功種出蔬菜。網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n德國科學家成功在南極嚴寒天氣下，種出首批不需泥土、日光與農藥的蔬菜，希望有助太空人將來在月球、火星等其他星球種植新鮮蔬果。<br />\n<br />\n德國位於南極的諾伊邁爾三號站的科學家，在室外溫度低於攝氏零下20度的嚴寒下，在高科技溫室內透過密封水循環及照明系統，成功種出3.6公斤（8磅）的沙律菜、18條青瓜和70條蘿蔔。<br />\n<br />\n協調今次研究的德國太空中心DLR說，到5月，科學家可望每星期有4至5公斤的水果和蔬菜收成。<br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署早前已成功在國際太空站種出蔬菜，參與DLR在南極計劃的舒伯特(Daniel Schubert)說，南極種植計劃的目的，是讓太空人將來在火星或月球種植出更多類型的蔬菜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180406/_2018040614345623089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180406%2F_2018040614345623089.jpg&h=e0229826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/683626-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E5%8D%97%E6%A5%B5%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%A8%AE%E8%8F%9C+%E5%86%80%E5%8A%A9%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%81%AB%E6%98%9F%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%AE%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F683626-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E8%258F%259C%2B%25E5%2586%2580%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2581%25AB%25E6%